snippet.title: Ein's Sword | ON Steam Game
snippet.description:
Simple field battles and training. Defeat enemies that appear in the field and obtain ability points every time you level up. Raise your preferred status and advance the battle to an advantage. Easy to use and comfortable to play. 

https://store.steampowered.com/app/2054760/Eins_Sword/
